{
  "texts": [
    "Disadvantages of deploying LLMs in math education.",
    "(i) Potential for misinterpretation.",
    "Misinterpretation of students' queries or errors in providing explanations by LLMs could lead to confusion.",
    "Inaccurate responses might result in the reinforcement of misconceptions, impacting the quality of education (Yen and Hsu, 2023).",
    "(ii) Limited understanding of individual learning styles."
  ]
}